LKN KH-'aMUr YHVH TShB'aVTh 'yL-HNB'aYM HNNY M'aKYL 'aVThM L'yNH VHShQThYM MY-Ur'aSh KY M'aTh NBY'aY YUrVShLM YTSh'aH ChNPhH LKL-H'aUrTSh.
